{"tid":1740100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Poly]皇上：國師不用食藥，國師是醫你的藥","createTime":"2019-11-19T23:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:50:57.000Z","uid":163207,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6b50e1d78f0d256fd50fccd4c4acc6e59f136d","tid":1740100,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T23:56:56.000Z","msg":"這位網友抱住救到一個得一個嘅心態，不斷努力推廣國師 Wan Chin 的策略與智慧，結果反而被排斥被踢走，這是必然的，忠言多數逆耳，苦口才是良藥。<br />\n他雖然付上代價，但也有收穫，在最危險的時間救了兩人。<br />\n<br />\n這位網友不是什麼KOL或文人，但他卻懂得分辨哪些難聽意見能救命，那些漂亮說話會害死人。<br />\n<br />\n相反，這幾日，我看見身邊那些文人、設計師、評論人，每天都在發表一些浪漫感性宣言⋯⋯然後話國師未食藥⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n國師不用食藥，國師是醫你的藥，但診金很高昂：你的自尊自大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RHNRcVb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRHNRcVb.jpg&h=2483d96c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91d442a5b530cd9f5aa8c529b917e2d325991e82","tid":1740100,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMUjfFK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMUjfFK.jpg&h=608c602b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fL6E7q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fL6E7q.png&h=6b02b283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KBYwec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KBYwec.png&h=debc8f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyKvnkU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyKvnkU.png&h=6a8ecacd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UzvnkX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UzvnkX.png&h=20a3054a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDgqbei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDgqbei.jpg&h=7a763e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2HME7F.png\" data-thum